3. Set Up Controllers and Routes:

   Generate controllers for your models and define routes in config/routes.rb.

4. Implement CRUD Operations:

   In your controllers, implement CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.

5. Test Endpoints:

   Use tools like Postman or curl to test your API endpoints.
   Test your endpoints with your Vue.js frontend to ensure they work together.

